{"id":"0fa37b4a4c485eb79e5a3f7374704be347a7344b","axis":"silent","repo":"duckdb/duckdb","sha":"0fa37b4a4c485eb79e5a3f7374704be347a7344b","parsed":{"files":[{"path":"extension/parquet/include/reader/variant/parquet_variant_iterator.hpp","lines":["@@ -0,0 +1,256 @@","+//===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//","+//                         DuckDB","+//","+// reader/variant/parquet_variant_iterator.hpp","+//","+//","+//===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//","+","+#pragma once","+","+#include \"duckdb/common/types/variant.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/types/variant_iterator.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/vector/vector_iterator.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/vector/unified_vector_format.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/optional_ptr.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/unique_ptr.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/common/helper.hpp\"","+#include \"duckdb/function/scalar_function.hpp\"","+#include \"reader/variant/variant_binary_decoder.hpp\"","+","+namespace duckdb {","+","+struct VariantBuilder;","+","+//! A \"group\" in the Parquet shredded VARIANT layout: STRUCT(value BLOB, [typed_value <T>]).","+//! The recursive view builds the (type-specific) VectorIterators of the group tree once, so each layer","+//! can be navigated by index during the (per-row) single-pass conversion.","+enum class ParquetGroupKind : uint8_t { LEAF, OBJECT, ARRAY };","+","+struct ShreddedGroupView {","+\t//! 'value' (the binary-encoded fallback / overlay)","+\tunique_ptr<VectorIterator<string_t>> value;","+","+\t//! Whether the group has a 'typed_value' (a shredded representation)","+\tbool has_typed_value = false;","+\tParquetGroupKind kind = ParquetGroupKind::LEAF;","+\tLogicalType typed_type;","+","+\t//! LEAF: the typed primitive values (type-erased; read typed via GetData<T> where T is known)","+\tUnifiedVectorFormat leaf_format;","+","+\t//! ARRAY: the list entries + the element (group) sub-view","+\tunique_ptr<VectorIterator<list_entry_t>> list;","+\tunique_ptr<ShreddedGroupView> element;","+","+\t//! OBJECT: the struct's validity + the field names + their (group) sub-views","+\tunique_ptr<VectorValidityIterator> typed_validity;","+\tvector<string> field_names;","+\tvector<unique_ptr<ShreddedGroupView>> fields;","+","+\t//! Build the view recursively from a group Vector","+\tvoid Build(Vector &group);","+};","+","+class ParquetVariantIterator;","+class ParquetObjectIterator;","+class ParquetArrayIterator;","+","+//! A lightweight cursor pointing at a single logical Parquet VARIANT value. A value is either SHREDDED","+//! (a position in a typed vector tree) or BINARY (a Spark variant-encoded value at a byte offset in a","+//! 'value' blob). Both expose the same node concept, so the shared EmitIterator traverses them uniformly","+//! and emits the correct VariantLogicalType.","+class ParquetVariantNode {","+public:","+\tenum class Kind : uint8_t { NULL_VALUE, MISSING, SHREDDED, BINARY };","+","+public:","+\tParquetVariantNode() : kind(Kind::NULL_VALUE) {","+\t}","+","+public:","+\tstatic ParquetVariantNode MakeNull() {","+\t\treturn ParquetVariantNode(Kind::NULL_VALUE);","+\t}","+\tstatic ParquetVariantNode MakeMissing() {","+\t\treturn ParquetVariantNode(Kind::MISSING);","+\t}","+\t//! A position in the shredded (typed) tree. 'overlay' is the binary OBJECT holding the leftover fields","+\t//! of a partially-shredded object (or null when fully shredded / not an object); 'overlay_end' is one","+\t//! past the end of the overlay's 'value' blob (for bounds-checking the binary reads).","+\tstatic ParquetVariantNode MakeShredded(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const ShreddedGroupView &view,","+\t                                       idx_t index, const_data_ptr_t overlay = nullptr,","+\t                                       const_data_ptr_t overlay_end = nullptr) {","+\t\tParquetVariantNode result(Kind::SHREDDED);","+\t\tresult.state = &state;","+\t\tresult.view = &view;","+\t\tresult.index = index;","+\t\tresult.binary = overlay;","+\t\tresult.binary_end = overlay_end;","+\t\treturn result;","+\t}","+\t//! A Spark variant-encoded value starting at 'data' (its header byte); 'end' is one past the end of the","+\t//! 'value' blob the value lives in (for bounds-checking the binary reads).","+\tstatic ParquetVariantNode MakeBinary(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const_data_ptr_t data,","+\t                                     const_data_ptr_t end) {","+\t\tParquetVariantNode result(Kind::BINARY);","+\t\tresult.state = &state;","+\t\tresult.binary = data;","+\t\tresult.binary_end = end;","+\t\treturn result;","+\t}","+","+public:","+\tbool IsNull() const {","+\t\treturn kind == Kind::NULL_VALUE;","+\t}","+\tbool IsMissing() const {","+\t\treturn kind == Kind::MISSING;","+\t}","+","+\tVariantLogicalType GetTypeId() const;","+\t//! Returns the fixed-width primitive payload (loaded / re-encoded as T)","+\ttemplate <class T>","+\tT GetData() const;","+\tstring_t GetString() const;","+\tVariantDecimalProperties GetDecimalProperties() const;","+\tParquetObjectIterator GetObjectChildren(VariantIterationOrder order) const;","+\tParquetArrayIterator GetArrayChildren() const;","+","+private:","+\texplicit ParquetVariantNode(Kind kind) : kind(kind) {","+\t}","+","+private:","+\tKind kind;","+\toptional_ptr<const ParquetVariantIterator> state;","+\t//! SHREDDED: the shredded position","+\toptional_ptr<const ShreddedGroupView> view;","+\tidx_t index = 0;","+\t//! SHREDDED OBJECT: the (binary) overlay object holding leftover fields, or null.","+\t//! BINARY: the value's start (header byte).","+\tconst_data_ptr_t binary = nullptr;","+\t//! One past the end of the 'value' blob 'binary' points into (for bounds-checking the binary reads)","+\tconst_data_ptr_t binary_end = nullptr;","+};","+","+//! A single (key, value) entry of an OBJECT","+struct ParquetObjectEntry {","+\tstring_t key;","+\tParquetVariantNode value;","+};","+","+//! Iterates the (key, value) children of an OBJECT: for a shredded object, the typed struct fields merged","+//! with the leftover (binary overlay) fields - deduplicated (typed fields win) and sorted lexicographically;","+//! for a binary object, the encoded fields.","+class ParquetObjectIterator {","+public:","+\t//! Shredded object (typed fields + optional binary overlay)","+\tParquetObjectIterator(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const ShreddedGroupView &view, idx_t index,","+\t                      const_data_ptr_t overlay, const_data_ptr_t overlay_end);","+\t//! Binary object","+\tParquetObjectIterator(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const VariantMetadata &metadata, const_data_ptr_t data,","+\t                      const_data_ptr_t end);","+","+public:","+\tconst ParquetObjectEntry *begin() const { // NOLINT: match stl API","+\t\treturn ordered_entries.data();","+\t}","+\tconst ParquetObjectEntry *end() const { // NOLINT: match stl API","+\t\treturn ordered_entries.data() + ordered_entries.size();","+\t}","+","+private:","+\tvoid Finalize();","+","+private:","+\tvector<ParquetObjectEntry> ordered_entries;","+};","+","+//! Iterates the element values of an ARRAY (shredded list or binary array). Random-access.","+class ParquetArrayIterator {","+public:","+\t//! Shredded array","+\tParquetArrayIterator(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const ShreddedGroupView &view, idx_t index);","+\t//! Binary array","+\tParquetArrayIterator(const ParquetVariantIterator &state, const VariantMetadata &metadata, const_data_ptr_t data,","+\t                     const_data_ptr_t end);","+","+public:","+\tidx_t size() const {","+\t\treturn length;","+\t}","+\tParquetVariantNode operator[](idx_t i) const;","+","+private:","+\treference<const ParquetVariantIterator> state;","+\tbool shredded;","+\tidx_t length;","+","+\t//! SHREDDED: the element (group) sub-view + the list offset of the elements","+\toptional_ptr<const ShreddedGroupView> element;","+\tidx_t base = 0;","+","+\t//! BINARY: where to read each element's value offset, and the values base","+\tconst_data_ptr_t field_offsets = nullptr;","+\tconst_data_ptr_t values = nullptr;","+\t//! BINARY: one past the end of the 'value' blob (for bounds-checking the binary reads)","+\tconst_data_ptr_t binary_end = nullptr;","+\tuint32_t field_offset_size = 0;","+};","+","+//! Iterates a shredded Parquet VARIANT column (metadata + group), handing out ParquetVariantNode cursors","+//! per row. Binary (Spark-encoded) values are read directly from the 'value' blobs; fixed-width payloads","+//! are fetched by value (no materialization).","+class ParquetVariantIterator {","+public:","+\tParquetVariantIterator(Vector &metadata, Vector &group);","+\t//! Binary-only: each row is a full Spark variant-encoded value (the metadata blob immediately followed","+\t//! by the value blob). There is no shredded group - the value is read right after the metadata.","+\texplicit ParquetVariantIterator(Vector &metadata);","+","+public:","+\t//! Reset the per-row state (lazily-decoded metadata) for a new row","+\tvoid BeginRow(idx_t row);","+\t//! Resolve the root value of 'row' (a missing root is promoted to a SQL NULL)","+\tParquetVariantNode Root(idx_t row) const;","+\t//! Resolve the root of a binary-only row: the value blob starts right after the metadata","+\tParquetVariantNode BinaryRoot() const;","+\t//! Resolve the value of the group 'view' at logical position 'index'","+\tParquetVariantNode ResolveGroup(const ShreddedGroupView &view, idx_t index) const;","+","+\t//! The (lazily-decoded) Variant metadata of the current row","+\tconst VariantMetadata &GetMetadata() const;","+","+private:","+\tShreddedGroupView root_view;","+","+\tVectorIterator<string_t> metadata;","+","+\tidx_t current_row = 0;","+\tmutable unique_ptr<VariantMetadata> current_metadata;","+};","+","+//! BuildVariant source wrapping a ParquetVariantIterator (mirrors VariantIteratorSource in core)","+struct ParquetVariantIteratorSource {","+\texplicit ParquetVariantIteratorSource(ParquetVariantIterator &iterator) : iterator(iterator) {","+\t}","+\tbool Emit(idx_t row, VariantBuilder &builder);","+","+\tParquetVariantIterator &iterator;","+};","+","+//! Convert a shredded Parquet VARIANT (metadata + group) into the canonical VARIANT 'result' in a single","+//! pass through the shared VariantBuilder","+class ParquetVariantConversion {","+public:","+\tstatic void Convert(Vector &metadata, Vector &group, Vector &result, idx_t count);","+\t//! Convert binary Variant values (each row being the metadata blob followed by the value blob) into the","+\t//! canonical VARIANT 'result' in a single pass","+\tstatic void ConvertBinary(Vector &metadata_and_value, Vector &result, idx_t count);","+\t//! 'variant_bytes_to_variant': decode a binary Variant value (metadata followed by value) into a VARIANT.","+\t//! The inverse of 'variant_to_parquet_variant'.","+\tstatic ScalarFunction GetBytesToVariantFunction();","+};","+","+} // namespace duckdb"],"additions":256,"deletions":0,"truncated":false},{"path":"extension/parquet/include/reader/variant/variant_binary_decoder.hpp","lines":["@@ -5,16 +5,11 @@"," #include <string>"," "," #include \"duckdb/common/types/string_type.hpp\"","-#include \"duckdb/common/types/value.hpp\"","-#include \"duckdb/common/types/variant_value.hpp\"","-#include \"yyjson.hpp\""," #include \"duckdb/common/exception.hpp\""," #include \"duckdb/common/string.hpp\""," #include \"duckdb/common/typedefs.hpp\""," #include \"duckdb/common/vector.hpp\""," ","-using namespace duckdb_yyjson;","-"," namespace duckdb {"," "," //! ------------ Metadata ------------","@@ -122,40 +117,4 @@ struct VariantValueMetadata {"," \tbool is_large;"," };"," ","-struct VariantDecodeResult {","-public:","-\tVariantDecodeResult() = default;","-\t~VariantDecodeResult() {","-\t\tif (doc) {","-\t\t\tyyjson_mut_doc_free(doc);","-\t\t}","-\t\tif (data) {","-\t\t\tfree(data);","-\t\t}","-\t}","-","-public:","-\tyyjson_mut_doc *doc = nullptr;","-\tch